[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       6[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       7[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Setup
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       8[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       9[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```bash
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      10[0m:[38;5;10m[49m pip install boto3 numpy
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      12[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      13[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Your environment needs credentials configured with permissions for `s3:GetObject`, `s3:PutObject`, `sagemaker:CreateTrainingJob`, `sagemaker:CreateEndpoint`, `sagemaker:InvokeEndpoint`, `dynamodb:PutItem`, `dynamodb:GetItem`, and `cloudwatch:PutMetricData`. You'll need a signed BAA because even de-identified ICU trajectory data is treated as PHI in most institutional policies.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      14[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
